  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the clinical safety and effectiveness of the Trifecta
      valve.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The clinical investigation is a multi-center, multi-country, prospective, non-randomized,
      observational study designed to evaluate the safety and effectiveness of the Trifecta valve.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
